  ✓ Screen the three allowed NS-specific candidates against the Tao gate and coefficient-shrinkage requirement
  ✓ Write REPORT.md incrementally with formulas, findings, and dead ends
  ✓ Write REPORT-SUMMARY.md with the final decision memo
